high_descs: Go to the left to stand on the right side of the sink.
Pick the fork up from the right side of the sink.
Put the fork in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the fork back up.
Back up and face the drawer farthest to the right.
Open the drawer and put the fork in and shut the door again.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.

high_descs: Look down, look right, walk straight, turn right when you reach the kitchen island, walk straight to the counter, turn left to face the kitchen island again, walk straight then right to face the sink and look down to the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Place the fork inside the sink, turn on the faucet, fill the sink with water, turn off the faucet, pick up the clean fork and look up.
Turn around, walk to the island, turn left, walk to the door, turn left to face the counter.
Open the drawer, place the fork inside, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the fork on the counter, that is in front of the paper towel holder.
Place the fork in the sink, between the vase and the spoon, turn the water on, rinse the fork, turn the water off, and remove the fork from the sink.
Go to the furthest end of the counter to your right.
Place the fork in the top drawer, under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.
